{"type": "article", "id": 60032, "title": "《神秘博士》中国风插画，苹果在CES主会场旁边打广告暗讽Android | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人的一切", "date": "2019-01-07T05:18:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 2413, "name": "logo"}, {"id": 68, "name": "苹果"}, {"id": 5880, "name": "今日头条"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1480589, "comment_count": 20, "praise_count": 48, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190107123550r5lBwWZaSdFLubK8.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p line=\"UwfN\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4325735646233484?#&amp;video\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>良品铺子宣布吴亦凡为品牌代言人。</b></a>广告片反复强调品牌是高端零食，有品味。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=e0824zdoc2e\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><h3><b>值得一看的 Case</b></h3><p line=\"I2WC\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4325735622194079?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>百事可乐推出京东 Joy 定制罐，</b></a>还推出限量抢券活动，就是反馈寥寥。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190107123655bC8RkVi9nY1U24Fx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.645570\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"CFFR\">苹果在 CES 主会场建筑 LVCC 旁边的一幢建筑外墙上，立起了高达数层的巨幅广告。广告左侧写着：<a href=\"https://appleinsider.com/articles/19/01/04/apple-plasters-privacy-ad-on-billboard-near-las-vegas-convention-center-ahead-of-ces\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>“你的 iPhone 发生什么，都会留在你自己的 iPhone 上。”</b></a>下侧是导向苹果官网隐私保护介绍页的链接。右侧则是 iPhone XS 的背面。暗讽安卓系统存在隐私安全隐患。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190107123711NcM8k6IEYXheZx2r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.612121\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"z9kf\">非盈利组织 Street Grace 总部位于亚特兰大，针对每年有超过 3600 名儿童在佐治亚州被卖为性奴隶的情况，它发起了一项活动，于是它发起了一项活动，找来 72&nbsp; 辆校车，<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_E_gayhKpVE\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">组成长达一英里的移动广告牌，</a>因为 3600 人可以填满 72 辆校车<b>，</b>以此传递呼吁停止人口贩卖的信息。</p><p line=\"O4aa\">这次活动的主题是是 Stop Traffick（停止贩卖），traffick 和 traffic 发音相近，词组含义一语双关，既是停止交通（畅通），也是停止贩卖（人口）。代理商是 BBDO 亚特兰大。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=t0824nx31s7\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"IRFN\" class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/BqYPu3eh3Gn/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>《神秘博士》发布了一系列中国风插画，</b></a>既有长城和三潭映月等著名景点，也有城市地标建筑如上海东方明珠和广州小蛮腰。插画由设计师 Richard Solomon 和阮菲菲 （Feifei Ruan）绘制。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201901071241269N8DJTQOsUCtEPgF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.720635\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190107124051KgamJICGLVZSfUtP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.720635\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190107124057ce5HEJzhjAGuBT2n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.720635\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190107124058qRiyTscW317JldZG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.720635\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190107124058xQwBEkLWsFCv5h0X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.720635\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190107124059a6Xu5DU8nWpJwb2N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.387302\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"1uH2\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5NTAwMjAyMA==&amp;mid=2697229267&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=682ac112a00a2a0acf1d30233d8cc76c&amp;chksm=83cff018b4b8790e9cdac68c703dbb4cc943a39f09a62c75a21252d786b8f66e5c78c76e7504&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=0107MS4Iz6VjAuLoY7tyXe3M&amp;key=5546231b29f22829484fc7f0c97a92529de940c80aa7cf63ebb31a8e19f5720c72a623acd860c424e97fb755070cffa64fdeb037cb6f56c6e4504e5d621dc8678007c9c25991abefee0735689958f2c7&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14+build(18A391)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=ks%2FZDQeVUxF51br71L9DFzCJbnCApFnTAfhjygRVhWHUDzMKioX4qZ1Cufl7iKxj\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>支付宝制作了一张长图“山海瑞兽图”，</b></a>描绘了 10 种神兽，每一种分别代表支付宝的一种功能，例如自拍证件照、刷码乘车等等，传递“科技暖人心”的理念。</p><p line=\"1uH2\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5ODEyOTAyMA==&amp;mid=2661915371&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=c598f903099c7579224fb4ff3cfc4d43&amp;chksm=bd9246f88ae5cfeedd49a93a43cb6ae4ee69f5930ab1f16753183b55fd94fa99600fe6b99a38&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=0107WwGuhAtGnQR1ymbZsor7&amp;key=ad91e5c59693255a515e2521f9d3225f99e41fa9d7780f5004ab6cd9299477c56f78389867da36e431ef1f9004b875fb286dae52b3c851b1821d745448cff121e5d3ce016a0791ccb8d95e9564906cc7&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14+build(18A391)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=ks%2FZDQeVUxF51br71L9DFzCJbnCApFnTAfhjygRVhWHUDzMKioX4qZ1Cufl7iKxj\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><b>今日头条换了新 Logo，</b></a>最明显的变化是去除了象征报纸的灰色底板。此外颜色和字体都有细微调整。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201901071242485wPT1xbtSF9EkloB.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.582407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"YlcL\"><a href=\"https://36kr.com/p/5170815.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>宜家在台湾闹市区开了两家“十元店”，</b></a>销售品类和名创优品的店面相似，大多是生活中的居家小物件，集中了宜家传统卖场里面的底价商品。不过这两家是快闪店，只营业至 2019 年 4 月。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190107124319qLNufg3Okp1xeA5S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190107124348dz0ENG28yq9RbScQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190107124414akqLJY07I1RrEuxt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><h3>其他，也很重要</h3><p line=\"NiJv\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4325201434543541?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>故宫彩妆面世不到一个月，全线停产下架。</b></a>部分消费者收到商品后反馈外观和品质不佳。比如口红外壳廉价感，膏体质地不够顺滑，蓝色点翠实用性不高等等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190107124559fTnzwRIivHLS0y3o.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.274021\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"bo9K\"><b><a href=\"https://www.foxnews.com/opinion/why-lord-taylors-fifth-avenue-store-closing-is-tragic-especially-for-this-former-employee\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">百货公司</a><a href=\"https://www.foxnews.com/opinion/why-lord-taylors-fifth-avenue-store-closing-is-tragic-especially-for-this-former-employee\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"> </a><a href=\"https://www.foxnews.com/opinion/why-lord-taylors-fifth-avenue-store-closing-is-tragic-especially-for-this-former-employee\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Lord</a><a href=\"https://www.foxnews.com/opinion/why-lord-taylors-fifth-avenue-store-closing-is-tragic-especially-for-this-former-employee\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"> &amp; Ta</a><a href=\"https://www.foxnews.com/opinion/why-lord-taylors-fifth-avenue-store-closing-is-tragic-especially-for-this-former-employee\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">ylor</a><a href=\"https://www.foxnews.com/opinion/why-lord-taylors-fifth-avenue-store-closing-is-tragic-especially-for-this-former-employee\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"> 纽约</a><a href=\"https://www.foxnews.com/opinion/why-lord-taylors-fifth-avenue-store-closing-is-tragic-especially-for-this-former-employee\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">第五</a><a href=\"https://www.foxnews.com/opinion/why-lord-taylors-fifth-avenue-store-closing-is-tragic-especially-for-this-former-employee\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">大</a><a href=\"https://www.foxnews.com/opinion/why-lord-taylors-fifth-avenue-store-closing-is-tragic-especially-for-this-former-employee\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">道旗舰店</a><a href=\"https://www.foxnews.com/opinion/why-lord-taylors-fifth-avenue-store-closing-is-tragic-especially-for-this-former-employee\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">正</a><a href=\"https://www.foxnews.com/opinion/why-lord-taylors-fifth-avenue-store-closing-is-tragic-especially-for-this-former-employee\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">式关门。</a></b>不过其余 45 家小型商场将继续营业。接下来 Lord &amp; Taylor 将向线上转型，除了官网之外，还会通过沃尔玛网站销售。</p><p line=\"bo9K\" class=\"\">题图来自：&nbsp;<a href=\"https://unsplash.com/photos/AYTMVeGXG8w?utm_source=unsplash&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_content=creditCopyText\" rel=\"nofollow\">Vitchakorn Koonyosying</a> on <a href=\"https://unsplash.com/search/photos/nuts?utm_source=unsplash&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_content=creditCopyText\" rel=\"nofollow\">Unsplash</a></p>"}